<section>
<title>Description détaillée</title>

<para>String utility.</para>

<para>This class is mainly used to implement the &apos;text-match&apos; filter, used by both the CalDAV calendar-query REPORT, and CardDAV addressbook-query REPORT. Because they both need it, it was decided to put it in Sabre\DAV instead.</para>

