    <title>ensureUTF8()</title>
<indexterm><primary>ensureUTF8</primary><secondary>StringUtil</secondary></indexterm>
<indexterm><primary>StringUtil</primary><secondary>ensureUTF8</secondary></indexterm>
<para><computeroutput>static ensureUTF8 ( $input)<computeroutput>[static]</computeroutput></computeroutput></para>
<para>This method takes an input string, checks if it&apos;s not valid UTF-8 and attempts to convert it to UTF-8 if it&apos;s not.</para>

<para>Note that currently this can only convert ISO-8859-1 to UTF-8 (latin-1), anything else will likely fail.</para>

